title: 吸热散热
question:
heat is released into the surroundings / 
haba dibebaskan ke persekitaran

heat is absorbed from the surroundings / 
haba diserap dari persekitaran

the water in the container becomes hot / 
air di dalam bekas menjadi panas

the water in the container becomes cold / 
air di dalam bekas menjadi sejuk

Surrounding tenperature decrease / 
Suhu sekeliling menurun

Surrounding tenperature increase / 
Suhu sekeliling meningkat
